Auto Lead conversion Basics

Trigger lead conversion based on:
* Configurable criteria for what should trigger the Conversion. Process builder entrance criteria approach.
* OR: Direct trigger (Approachable via PB, Flow, Apex, REST API)

Configurable what happens during/afer the conversion e.g.
* Create contact and account
* Set Record types (household)
* Create an opportunity
* Create Recurring gift
* ? Conditional config based on criteria on the Lead (e.g. Based on field on Lead create Opp. OR not)
